dc_title_s: Atlas and Farm Directory with Complete Survey in Township Plats, Lincoln County, Minnesota
dc_description_s: Atlas and farm directory with complete survey in township plats, Lincoln County, Minnesota, containing plats of all townships with owners' names, also Minnesota state map showing automobile roads, maps of the United States and the world, an outline map of the county showing the location of townships, villages, roads, schools, churches, railroads and streams.|31 x 41 entimeters|Scale [1:42,240]|Minnesota County Maps, Plat Books, and Atlases
